Run command for run the test case for specific browser from config file also specific project
npx playwright test /tests/PageTest/blazeTest.spec.js --config playwright.configMobile.js --project=Chrome

Run commad for all test
npx playwright test

Run commad for specific test case with (single test file)
npx playwright test /tests/PageTest/blazeTest.spec.js

Run a set of test files
npx playwright test tests/todo-page/ tests/landing-page/

Run tests that are in line 42 in my-spec.ts
npx playwright test my-spec.ts:42

Run the test with the title
npx playwright test -g "add a todo item"

Run tests in headed browsers
npx playwright test --headed

Run in debug mode with Playwright Inspector
npx playwright test --debug

Run tests in interactive UI mode, with a built-in watch mode (Preview)
npx playwright test --ui


